    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s looking for a great new home. It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in wonderful shape, perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! The interior is clean, it drives like a dream, and it\u2019s been really well-cared for over the years. You\u2019re going to love how it handles on the road! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
