    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. This example features a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential for precise power delivery. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and upgraded with Bilstein dampers to sharpen turn-in response. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and rod bearing inspection, ensuring the internal reciprocating assembly is within spec. The exterior retains its factory aerodynamic profile with minor patina consistent with enthusiast use, while the interior remains a focused cockpit for the spirited driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
