    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving peak, powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The power is sent to the rear wheels via a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable Differential Lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a documented rear subframe reinforcement and a recent VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal cam timing. The valvetrain has been shimmed to factory specifications within the last 5,000 miles. While showing minor road wear consistent with its mileage, the chassis remains exceptionally rigid with refreshed bushings and a balanced damping profile, offering the precise turn-in and tactile feedback this platform is renowned for.",
